The overall impression hasn't changed. Lifting of measures has been accompanied by increases in locally acquired infections through increasing clusters related to gatherings of people at employment (bringing it outside employment to contacts) and in houses of worship, and bars and clubs. However, that being said, importations are also playing a major role in the country as well. The increase in cases in the past few days has been paralleled by increases in reported deaths.

